---
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
import Prose from '../Prose.astro';
---

<!-- NEW SECTION 4: KAIWA TRAP / FOSSILIZATION (Biohazard Theme) -->
<section class='py-20 lg:py-32 relative'>
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10'>
    <div
      class='relative md:bg-[oklch(0.112_0_0)] md:rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden md:border md:border-orange-500/20 md:shadow-2xl transition-all md:hover:border-orange-500/40'
    >
      <!-- Background Hazard Stripes -->
      <div
        class='absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none hidden md:block'
        style='background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, oklch(0% 0 0deg) 0, oklch(0% 0 0deg) 10px, oklch(87.9% 0.176 91deg) 10px, oklch(87.9% 0.176 91deg) 20px);'
      >
      </div>

      <div class='py-10 md:px-20 md:py-24 relative z-10'>
        <!-- Header: WARNING -->
        <div class='text-center mb-16'>
          <div
            class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/30 text-orange-500 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 animate-pulse'
          >
            ⚠ BIOHAZARD // COGNITIVE DAMAGE
          </div>
          <h2
            class='text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-4'
          >
            Gimana Latihan KAIWA? <br />
            <span
              class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600'
              >Toxic untuk Pemula.</span
            >
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-20 items-start p-4'>
          <!-- Left Column: The Specimen (Vertical Manga) -->
          <div class='relative group'>
            <!-- Glass Containment Unit Frame -->
            <div
              class='absolute -inset-2 md:-inset-4 bg-orange-500/5 border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm -z-10'
            >
            </div>
            <!-- Caution Tape Decorations -->
            <div
              class='absolute -top-1 -left-1 md:-top-2 md:-left-2 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-orange-500/50 rounded-tl-xl pointer-events-none'
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class='absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 md:-bottom-2 md:-right-2 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-orange-500/50 rounded-br-xl pointer-events-none'
            >
            </div>

            <div
              class='rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl relative'
            >
              <CldImage
                src='Manga_Fosilisasi_Kaiwa_Generated_Image_5psn085psn085psn_btvslb'
                width={1792}
                height={2400}
                alt='Ilustrasi Fosilisasi Kaiwa'
                class='w-full h-auto object-cover filter contrast-125 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700'
              />
              <!-- Overlay Text -->
              <div
                class='absolute bottom-4 right-4 text-orange-500/50 font-mono text-xs rotate-90 origin-bottom-right'
              >
                FIG 1.0: PREMATURE OUTPUT
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column: The Diagnosis -->
          <div class='prose-lg prose-invert text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
            <p class='lead text-lg md:text-xl text-white font-bold'>
              Mungkin guru les atau temen kamu pernah bilang: <span
                class='text-orange-400'
                ><i
                  >"Ayo, latihan kaiwa! Ngomong aja dulu, jangan takut salah!"</i
                ></span
              >
            </p>

            <p>
              Kedengarannya motivasi banget, ya? Tapi sebenarnya, nasihat kayak
              gitu bisa bikin lebih banyak mudarat daripada manfaat, terutama
              kalau kamu masih pemula.
            </p>

            <p>
              Kenapa? Karena kalau kamu dipaksa ngomong (output) sebelum otakmu
              dapet cukup input—yaitu nyerap bahasa lewat dengerin dan baca
              banyak—kamu nggak lagi "ngomong bahasa Jepang" beneran.
            </p>

            <p class='font-bold text-white! mb-2'>
              Kamu lagi main <span class='text-red-500'>sirkus</span> di otak sendiri:
            </p>

            <!-- SYSTEM OVERLOAD VISUALIZATION -->
            <div
              class='my-6 p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl bg-black border border-red-900/30 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shadow-inner relative overflow-hidden'
              aria-label='Visualisasi proses mental: langkah-langkah overload ketika dipaksa speaking terlalu dini'
            >
              <div
                class='absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 text-red-700 text-xs animate-pulse'
              >
                ● CPU OVERLOAD
              </div>
              <div class='space-y-2 md:space-y-3'>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2 md:gap-4 text-gray-500'>
                  <span class='text-red-500'>[STEP 0]</span>
                  <span>Mikir ide dulu dalam Bahasa Indonesia...</span>
                </div>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2 md:gap-4 text-orange-400'>
                  <span class='text-red-500'>[STEP 1]</span>
                  <span
                    >Nerjemahin ke rumus bunpou yang dihafal... <span
                      class='animate-pulse'>_</span
                    ></span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class='flex items-start gap-2 md:gap-4 text-orange-400'>
                  <span class='text-red-500'>[STEP 2]</span>
                  <span>Cari-cari kosakata yang pas...</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class='flex items-start gap-2 md:gap-4 text-red-500 font-bold'
                >
                  <span class='text-red-500'>[STEP 3]</span>
                  <span>Baru keluar dari mulut (Sering kacau).</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              Proses ini bikin otakmu kerja <strong>4 kali lipat</strong> lebih berat
              dibanding native speaker, yang langsung ngomong tanpa mikir rumus. Hasilnya?
              Ngomongmu jadi kaku, lambat, penuh jeda, dan aksennya medok Indonesia
              banget.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FULL WIDTH CONTENT: Manga & Risk Assessment -->
        <div class='mt-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-20'>
          <!-- RISK ASSESSMENT MODULE -->
          <div class='border-t border-dashed border-stone-800 pt-10'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 justify-center'>
              <div
                class='h-px w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent to-stone-700'
              >
              </div>
              <h3
                class='text-3xl font-black text-white tracking-widest uppercase flex items-center gap-3'
              >
                <span class='text-red-600 animate-pulse text-4xl'>⚠</span>
                Risk Assessment
              </h3>
              <div
                class='h-px w-12 bg-linear-to-l from-transparent to-stone-700'
              >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-8'>
              <!-- DANGER DATA: FOSSILIZATION -->
              <div
                class='relative p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-stone-800 hover:border-red-600 transition-colors group/danger'
              >
                <h4
                  class='font-mono text-xs text-stone-400 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2'
                >
                  <span class='w-2 h-2 bg-red-600 rounded-full'></span> Subject: Fossilization
                </h4>
                <p class='text-lg mb-4 text-stone-200'>
                  Kesalahan yang dipaksa keluar mengeras jadi kebiasaan
                  permanen.
                </p>

                <div
                  class='bg-black/50 p-3 rounded border border-white/5 font-mono text-xs text-stone-400 mb-4'
                >
                  <span class='text-red-500 font-bold'>STAT:</span> 95% learner failure
                  rate detected.
                </div>

                <!-- Research Quote Block -->
                <div
                  class='bg-black/40 border-l-2 border-red-900/50 p-4 rounded-r font-mono text-xs text-stone-400 leading-relaxed relative overflow-hidden group-hover/danger:border-red-600/50 transition-colors'
                >
                  <div
                    class='absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-30 text-red-500 text-[10px] tracking-widest'
                  >
                    [EXTRACT]
                  </div>
                  <p class='italic mb-3'>
                    "Temporary fossilization refers to the stagnant process in
                    which non-target factors are fixed in the target language... <span
                      class='text-red-400 font-bold bg-red-900/20 px-1'
                      >Research shows only 5% can reach the target language
                      while 95% can’t.</span
                    >"
                  </p>
                  <div
                    class='mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col gap-3'
                  >
                    <div
                      class='text-[10px] text-stone-600 uppercase flex items-center justify-between'
                    >
                      <span>Source: Qian, M., & Xiao, Z. (2010)</span>
                      <span>Vol. 3, No. 1</span>
                    </div>
                    <a
                      href='https://www.researchgate.net/publication/42386451_Strategies_for_Preventing_and_Resolving_Temporary_Fossilization_in_Second_Language_Acquisition'
                      target='_blank'
                      rel='noopener noreferrer'
                      class='inline-block opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity'
                    >
                      <img
                        src='/researchgate-logo-white.svg'
                        alt='Read on ResearchGate'
                        class='h-4'
                      />
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- MECHANISM: NEGATIVE TRANSFER -->
              <div
                class='relative p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-stone-800 hover:border-orange-500 transition-colors group/mech flex flex-col justify-between'
              >
                <div>
                  <h4
                    class='font-mono text-xs text-stone-400 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2'
                  >
                    <span class='w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full'></span>
                    Mechanism: Negative Transfer
                  </h4>
                  <div
                    class='rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/10 mb-4 w-full'
                  >
                    <CldImage
                      src='Manga_Fosilisasi_Kaiwa_v2_Generated_Image_5psn085psn085psn_zgmtlj'
                      width={1635}
                      height={1129}
                      alt='Ilustrasi Kerusakan Otak'
                      class='w-full h-auto object-contain opacity-80 group-hover/mech:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500'
                    />
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    Otak mencampur struktur Indonesia ke Jepang. Bahasa Jepang
                    jadi <span
                      class='line-through decoration-red-500/50 text-stone-500'
                      >distorsi</span
                    >.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- COMPARATIVE ANALYSIS: WITNESS LOG -->
            <div
              class='bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden mb-8'
            >
              <div class='absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-20'>
                <svg
                  class='w-24 h-24 text-white'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                  ><path
                    d='M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 14H9V8h2v8zm4 0h-2V8h2v8z'
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </div>
              <h4
                class='font-mono text-xs text-blue-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-blue-400/20 pb-2 inline-block'
              >
                Comparative Analysis // Witness Log
              </h4>
              <div class='grid gap-6 text-base'>
                <div class='flex gap-4 items-start'>
                  <div
                    class='text-emerald-400 font-bold w-20 shrink-0 tracking-wider'
                  >
                    NATIVE
                  </div>
                  <div class='text-stone-300'>
                    Kalau ragu, mereka <i>paraphrase</i> atau tolak halus ("Ano ne...").
                    Mereka menjaga <i>flow</i>.
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class='flex gap-4 items-start'>
                  <div
                    class='text-red-400 font-bold w-20 shrink-0 tracking-wider'
                  >
                    YOU
                  </div>
                  <div class='text-stone-300'>
                    Maksa pakai logika dewasa. Langsung tebas apa yang ada di
                    kepala meski <i>invalid syntax</i>.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SOLUTION: PROTOCOL UPDATE -->
            <div
              class='bg-emerald-900/10 border border-emerald-500/20 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden'
            >
              <div
                class='absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-3xl -mr-10 -mt-10'
              >
              </div>
              <h3
                class='text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 relative z-10'
              >
                <span class='w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse'
                ></span>
                Recommended Protocol
              </h3>
              <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 relative z-10'>
                <div>
                  <p class='mb-4 text-xl text-white font-bold'>
                    Peluk <span class='text-emerald-400'>Silent Period</span>.
                  </p>
                  <p class='text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed'>
                    Jangan paksa output. Biarkan otakmu mengumpulkan data pola
                    bahasa secara alami lewat input masif.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <ul class='space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-300'>
                  <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                    <span class='text-emerald-500 mt-1'>✓</span> Fokus input massal
                    (Podcast, Anime, Manga, dll)
                  </li>
                  <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                    <span class='text-emerald-500 mt-1'>✓</span> Berbicara seperlunya
                    seperti anak 3 tahun
                  </li>
                  <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                    <span class='text-emerald-500 mt-1'>✓</span> Biarkan grammar tumbuh
                    sendiri tanpa rumus
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
